    "permit_type": "Land Use ReviewType 2 procedureAD: Adjustment",
    "work_description": "Approval of an Adjustment to Zoning Code Section 33.110.225.B to increase the maximum building coverage on this site by 353 square feet, from 2,587 square feet to 2,940 square feet, per the approved plans, Exhibits C-1 and C-2, signed and dated September 20, 2024, subject to the following conditions: A.As part of the building permit application submittal, each of the required site plans and any additional drawings must reflect the information and design approved by this land use review as indicated in Exhibits C-1 and C-2. The sheets on which this information appears must be labeled, \"Proposal and design as approved in Case File # LU 24-069070 AD.¿ B.Prior to issuance of a building permit for the new garage/ADU building, the applicant must do one of the following: 1.Obtain an approved Driveway Design Exception from the Portland Bureau of Transportation for the new driveway on N Newman Avenue; or 2.Obtain final inspection approval of a permit to construct a new curb in front of the existing driveway on N Dwight Avenue.",
